#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kturtle; is an educational programming environment that uses <link linkend="
"\"what-is-turtlelang\">&turtlescript;</link>, a programming language loosely "
"based on and inspired by &logo;. The goal of &kturtle; is to make "
"programming as easy and accessible as possible. This makes &kturtle; "
"suitable for teaching kids the basics of math, geometry and... programming. "
"One of the main features of &turtlescript; is the ability to translate the "
"commands into the speaking language of the programmer."
msgstr ""
"&kturtle; je izobraževalno programsko okolje, ki uporablja <link linkend="
"\"what-is-turtlelang\">&turtlescript;</link>, programski jezik, ki delno "
"temelji na &logo; in ga navdihuje. Cilj &kturtle; je narediti programiranje "
"čim bolj enostavno in dostopno. Zaradi tega &kturtle; primeren za poučevanje "
"otrok osnov matematike, geometrije in ... programiranja. Ena od glavnih "
"funkcij &turtlescript; je zmožnost prevajanja ukazov v govorni jezik "
"programerja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kturtle; is named after <quote>the turtle</quote> that plays a central role "
"in the programming environment. The student will usually instruct the "
"turtle, using the &turtlescript; commands, to make a drawing on <link "
"linkend=\"the-canvas\">the canvas</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kturtle; je poimenovan po <quote>želvi</quote>, ki ima osrednjo vlogo v "
"programskem okolju. Učenec bo želvi običajno dal navodila z uporabo "
"&turtlescript; ukaze za risanje na <link linkend=\"the-canvas\">platnu</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is &turtlescript;?"
msgstr "Kaj je &turtlescript;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&turtlescript;, the programming language used in &kturtle;, is inspired by "
"the &logo; family of programming languages. The first version of &logo; was "
"created by Seymour Papert of MIT Artificial Intelligence Laboratory in 1967 "
"as an offshoot of the LISP programming language. From then many versions of "
"&logo; have been released. By 1980 &logo; was gaining momentum, with "
"versions for MSX, Commodore, Atari, Apple II and IBM PC systems. These "
"versions were mainly for educational purposes. The MIT is still maintains "
"<ulink url=\"https://el.media.mit.edu/logo-foundation/\">a website on &logo;"
"</ulink> containing a list of several popular implementation of the language."
msgstr ""
"&turtlescript;, programski jezik, ki se uporablja v &kturtle;, se zgleduje "
"po &logo; družino programskih jezikov. Prva različica &logo; je ustvaril "
"Seymour Papert iz Laboratorija za umetno inteligenco MIT leta 1967 kot odcep "
"programskega jezika LISP. Od takrat je veliko različic &logo; so bili "
"izpuščeni. Do leta 1980 &logo; je pridobival zagon z različicami za sisteme "
"MSX, Commodore, Atari, Apple II in IBM PC. Te različice so bile predvsem v "
"izobraževalne namene. MIT še vedno vzdržuje <ulink url=\"https://el.media."
"mit.edu/logo-foundation/\">spletno mesto na &logo;</ulink>, ki vsebuje "
"seznam več priljubljenih implementacij jezika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&turtlescript; shares a feature found in many other implementations of "
"&logo;: the ability to translate the commands to suit the native language of "
"the student. This feature makes it easier for students that have no or "
"little understanding of English to get started. Besides this feature "
"&kturtle; has <link linkend=\"features-of-kturtle\">many other features</"
"link> aimed at easing the students initial experience with programming."
msgstr ""
"&turtlescript; ima skupno lastnost, ki jo najdemo v mnogih drugih izvedbah "
"&logo;: zmožnost prevajanja ukazov, da ustrezajo materinemu jeziku študenta. "
"Ta funkcija študentom, ki ne razumejo angleščine, olajša začetek. Poleg te "
"funkcije &kturtle; ima <link linkend=\"features-of-kturtle\">številne druge "
"funkcije</link>, katerih cilj je študentom olajšati začetno izkušnjo s "
"programiranjem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Features of &kturtle;"
msgstr "Lastnosti &kturtle;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kturtle; has some nice features that make starting to program a breeze. See "
"here some of the highlights of &kturtle; feature set:"
msgstr ""
"&kturtle; ima nekaj lepih funkcij, zaradi katerih je začetek programiranja "
"preprost. Tukaj si oglejte nekaj vrhuncev &kturtle; nabor funkcij:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An integrated environment with &turtlescript; interpreter, <link linkend="
"\"the-editor\">editor</link>, <link linkend=\"the-canvas\">canvas</link> and "
"other tools all in one application (no extra dependencies)."
msgstr ""
"Integrirano okolje z &turtlescript; tolmač, <link linkend=\"the-editor"
"\">urejevalnik</link>, <link linkend=\"the-canvas\">platno</link> in druga "
"orodja v eni aplikaciji (brez dodatnih odvisnosti)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ability to translate the &turtlescript; commands using the translation "
"framework of &kde;."
msgstr ""
"Možnost prevajanja &turtlescript; ukaze z uporabo prevodnega ogrodja &kde;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&turtlescript; supports user defined functions, recursion and dynamic type "
"switching."
msgstr ""
"&turtlescript; podpira uporabniško določene funkcije, rekurzijo in dinamično "
"preklapljanje tipov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "The execution can be slowed down, paused or stopped at any time."
msgstr ""
"Izvedbo je mogoče kadar koli upočasniti, začasno ustaviti ali ustaviti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A powerful <link linkend=\"the-editor\">editor</link> featuring intuitive "
"syntax highlighting, line numbering, error markers, visual execution and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Zmogljiv <link linkend=\"the-editor\">urejevalnik</link> z intuitivnim "
"označevanjem sintakse, oštevilčevanjem vrstic, označevalci napak, vizualno "
"izvedbo in več."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"the-canvas\">canvas</link>, where the turtle draws, can "
"be printed or saved either as an image (PNG) or a drawing (&SVG;)."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"the-canvas\">platno</link>, kjer želva riše, lahko natisnete "
"ali shranite kot sliko (PNG) ali risbo (&SVG;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Context help: help where you need it. Just press <keysym>F2</keysym> (or see "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Help on: ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>) to get help on the piece of code currently under your cursor."
msgstr ""
"Kontekstna pomoč: pomoč, kjer jo potrebujete. Preprosto pritisnite "
"<keysym>F2</keysym> (ali glejte <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pomoč na: ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>), da dobite "
"pomoč za delček kode trenutno pod vašim kazalcem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An error dialog that links the error messages to the mistakes in the program "
"and marks them red."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno o napakah, ki poveže sporočila o napakah z napakami v "
"programu in jih označi rdeče."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simplified programming terminology."
msgstr "Poenostavljena programska terminologija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Integrated example programs to make it easy to get started. These examples "
"are translated using &kde; translation framework."
msgstr ""
"Integrirani primeri programov za lažji začetek. Ti primeri so prevedeni z "
"&kde; prevajalski okvir."

